{"tid":2014042,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係日本讀緊大學？","createTime":"2020-05-12T17:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T09:52:55.000Z","uid":156312,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"790750763fb7e135c347669400f41326332b41fe","tid":2014042,"uid":156312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始返左半個月學 <br />\n乜說明會迎生會都取消晒、入左學以嚟淨係去過大學1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好話日本朋友、留學生朋友都冇啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衣家日日online上堂、日文底又唔好、啲筆記深到屌出聲、老師講緊乜又唔係好聽得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱入學就開始擔心畢唔畢到業⋯<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣或者有過來人分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715c25ebc22bbcd52cb50e48fe34dc63267dd9c6","tid":2014042,"uid":123969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:41:31.000Z","msg":"你其他同學都係冇朋友㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7ab61221afcadc42774c358f6e9e738107d49c","tid":2014042,"uid":156312,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"715c25ebc22bbcd52cb50e48fe34dc63267dd9c6","tid":2014042,"uid":123969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:41:31.000Z","msg":"你其他同學都係冇朋友㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"佢地玩Twitter 玩到熟哂、每個學部都好似開左line group 內向毒撚又冇玩開Twitter得個睇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49da32c42c249df4ec94ee27e52c17bba736cef4","tid":2014042,"uid":156312,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"同埋我個學科得我一個留學生、其他學科起碼都有幾個中國同台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係話想埋堆圍威喂但衣家好冇安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1099e244a539feb8759a21f3a5f7426c0bff9336","tid":2014042,"uid":131121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"日文唔好都可以讀日本大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"749681a12327d31bef7d8c552e780dc59bd53e14","tid":2014042,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"ペアーズをダウンロードしてセフレを探して"},{"pid":"125f330388c633940b160b0d024785a79264c655","tid":2014042,"uid":156312,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1099e244a539feb8759a21f3a5f7426c0bff9336","tid":2014042,"uid":131121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"日文唔好都可以讀日本大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"絕對可以 讀語言學校見證住條中國人每日上堂打機訓教、放學不停打工、期末考重考4次先合格、講句完整句子都有困難既佢入左大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927f5a1320078ad7b729aca37088d0db7594c277","tid":2014042,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"你入到學算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下果d都唔知點算<br />\n家下6月果場EJU都取消埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0efc580c834eae0894000d9021d17d44953124b","tid":2014042,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:18:29.000Z","msg":"咁又真係慘d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34601df401ea1927c334b1319a2284e3e9829543","tid":2014042,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"927f5a1320078ad7b729aca37088d0db7594c277","tid":2014042,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"你入到學算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下果d都唔知點算<br />\n家下6月果場EJU都取消埋<img src=\"/ass